    <p style="font-size:12px;color:#9CA3AF;margin:0 0 12px;">What buyers type into the natural-language search — first-party intent data. "Demand gaps" are searches that returned zero matches: vehicles people wanted that we didn't have (a sourcing signal). Powers the P11 keep/drop review.</p>
    {searchTotal === 0 ? (
      <div style="font-size:13px;color:#9CA3AF;background:#fff;border:1px solid #E5E7EB;border-radius:12px;padding:16px;">No searches recorded in the last 30 days yet.</div>
    ) : (
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;">
